# Requirements

## Packaged Architecture
- x86_64 (tested; Docker image `liab-artifact.tar` provided)

## Software Requirements
- Docker 20.10+ with the current user having permissions to use the Docker daemon
- GNU Make 4.3+
- Linux/macOS/Windows

## Dependencies
All dependencies included in Docker image (`liab-artifact.tar`):
- Python 3.9
- Python requirements are further listed in `requirements.txt`
- a `Dockerfile` is also provided. The image can be built using `make build-docker`
